    # "{i}Daniel was already starting in, his voice a bit too cheerful for my liking.{/i}"
    "{i}Daniel já estava começando, sua voz um pouco alegre demais para o meu gosto.{/i}"

# game/story_scripts/day1_emma.rpy:368
