    # "{i}I kept my expression neutral, focusing on my plate, but inside, everything was swirling—frustration with Alex, irritation at Daniel, and now, Isabella.{/i}"
    "{i}Mantive minha expressão neutra, concentrando-me no meu prato, mas por dentro, tudo estava girando: frustração com Alex, irritação com Daniel e agora, Isabella.{/i}"

# game/story_scripts/day1_emma.rpy:393
