# game/story_scripts/day1_emma.rpy:395
translate portuguese day1_emma_1_602471c8:

    # a "So, there I was, trying to cut weight while also keeping my strength up. It was a nightmare."
    a "Então, lá estava eu, tentando perder peso e ao mesmo tempo manter minha força. Foi um pesadelo."

# game/story_scripts/day1_emma.rpy:396
translate portuguese day1_emma_1_665c0b3d:

    # isa "That must have been tough. How did you manage it?"
    isa "Deve ter sido difícil. Como você conseguiu?"

# game/story_scripts/day1_emma.rpy:397
translate portuguese day1_emma_1_8dadc8cf:

    # "{i}Of course, Isabella jumped in, her tone overly interested. She always had a way of sliding into conversations that didn’t concern her, especially when it involved Alex.{/i}"
    "{i}É claro que Isabella se intrometeu, seu tom excessivamente interessado. Ela sempre tinha um jeito de deslizar para conversas que não lhe diziam respeito, especialmente quando envolviam Alex.{/i}"

# game/story_scripts/day1_emma.rpy:398
translate portuguese day1_emma_1_78a79461:

    # "{i}I glanced up briefly to see her leaning in, her gaze fixed on him with that look—the one she used when she was playing at being flirty.{/i}"
    "{i}Olhei para cima brevemente e a vi se inclinando, seu olhar fixo nele com aquele olhar — o que ela usava quando estava brincando de flertar.{/i}"

# game/story_scripts/day1_emma.rpy:399
