    r "Com licença, Sr. Alex. Aqui está seu jantar."

# game/story_scripts/day1_emma.rpy:401
translate portuguese day1_emma_1_429ae141:

    # "{i}Ruby voice was polite, as always, though I could sense the discomfort in her posture, especially when she approached Daniel.{/i}"
    "{i}A voz de Ruby estava educada, como sempre, embora eu pudesse sentir o desconforto em sua postura, especialmente quando ela se aproximava de Daniel.{/i}"

# game/story_scripts/day1_emma.rpy:402
translate portuguese day1_emma_1_efd6f6ea:

    # a "Thanks for the food, Ruby."
    a "Obrigada pela comida, Ruby."

# game/story_scripts/day1_emma.rpy:403
translate portuguese day1_emma_1_6b0e0f1e:

    # "{i}I didn't miss the way Alex’s eyes drifted, but I chose to ignore it. Men would be men, right? Besides, Ruby had this presence—almost too warm, too inviting for her own good.{/i}"
    "{i}Não perdi a maneira como os olhos de Alex se desviaram, mas escolhi ignorar. Homens seriam homens, certo? Além disso, Ruby tinha essa presença — quase calorosa demais, convidativa demais para seu próprio bem.{/i}"

# game/story_scripts/day1_emma.rpy:404
translate portuguese day1_emma_1_6abaa864:

    # "{i}As she moved to serve Daniel, I knew what was coming before the words even left his mouth.{/i}"
    "{i}Quando ela se moveu para servir Daniel, eu sabia o que estava por vir antes mesmo que as palavras saíssem da boca dele.{/i}"

# game/story_scripts/day1_emma.rpy:406
